---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Prose from '../components/Prose.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — CosmoCrew"
  description="CosmoCrew is a small, independent, founder-led software studio building a few calm, well-made apps for iOS."
  path="about"
>
  <section class="container narrow">
    <div class="section-head">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>A small studio</h1>
    </div>

    <Prose>
      <p>
        CosmoCrew is a small, independent software studio. It is founder-led and
        deliberately modest — not a big company, and not trying to be one. The
        goal is simple: build a few genuinely good apps and look after them well.
      </p>
      <p>
        We like quiet software. Tools that do one thing clearly, run fast, and
        respect your attention instead of competing for it. That shapes how we
        work: we ship slowly, polish carefully, and would rather make a small
        number of things well than a long list of things in a hurry.
      </p>
      <p>
        Today two apps are live on iOS — <strong>SliceFocus</strong> for visual
        day planning and focus, and <strong>LexiPower</strong> for vocabulary
        practice. Each grew out of something we wanted to use ourselves, and each
        keeps getting better in small, steady steps.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you use one of our apps, thank you — it genuinely means a lot to a
        studio this size. You can always reach us at
        <a href="mailto:contact@cosmocrew.dev">contact@cosmocrew.dev</a>.
      </p>
    </Prose>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .narrow {
    max-width: var(--maxw-prose);
  }
</style>
